Use the standard library
This is how to specialFilter of nums:
   Remember that count is 0
   Remember that i is 0
   Do this nums's length times:
      Remember that n is item i in nums
      When n is more than 0, then:
         When remainder of n and 2 is not 0, then:
            When item 0 in (tostring of n) is item 0 in "5", then:
               When item (diff of (tostring of n)'s length and 1) in (tostring of n) is item 0 in "5", then:
                  Increase count
               End when
            End when
         End when
      End when
      Increase i
   End do
   The answer is count
